pps/2195790/extras/3_different_schools.png?t=1728903809\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195790/extras/CLA2_Map.jpg?t=1728903809\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This time there's different schools to visit and each school has its own host of interesting characters, and even more interesting courses which your students can take! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195790/extras/countless_combinations.png?t=1728903809\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195790/extras/CLA2_RaceCourses.jpg?t=1728903809\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With 10 different classes, 18 different courses, 3 different alignments, the possibilities for creating the perfect cast of students is seemingly endless. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195790/extras/Alchemy_recipes.png?t=1728903809\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195790/extras/CLA2_recipe_1.jpg?t=1728903809\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect recipes and get crafting! The items you find in the labyrinths can help you weather different storms.</p>","developers":["Zerodiv"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2195790/header.jpg?t=1728903809","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a92024 ACQUIRE Corp. All Rights Reserved. Published by PQube Limited.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257018322,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257018322/movie